    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-host001.m4a",
      "text": "新生・BIG4チャレンジ、今回の勝者は――\n王者っ、月のテンペストーーーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 11.046348548000001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8200
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13200
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 18966.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.2333326896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさま、応援ありがとうございます！　挑戦して\nくれた方々にも盛大な拍手をお願いいたします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2333326896,
      "endTime": 20.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-03.m4a",
          "delay": 12599.998982800002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-03.m4a",
          "delay": 12399.998982800002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 22.4166646242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "かんぱーーーーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4666646242,
      "endTime": 25.2866646767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.4444194237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "今回も、素晴らしいバトルでしたわね\nまさか『DayDream』が挑んでくださるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4444194237,
      "endTime": 33.050201741799995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.2444194237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんから、BIG4チャレンジを復活させたい\nって言われた時は、驚いちゃったけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2444194237,
      "endTime": 39.654963628400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.84194777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんとの戦いで、気付いたことがあったから\n苦しくても、怖くても、挑戦することに意味がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.84194777,
      "endTime": 48.776845955800006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.9752811033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私達の勇気が、誰かを照らす光になるんだ、って\nもちろん、負ける可能性がないとは言えないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9752811033,
      "endTime": 57.933036001299996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.14194777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "もし負けても、その時はまた頑張ればいい\n私達なら大丈夫って、芽衣もあの時言ってくれたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.14194777,
      "endTime": 67.4919479608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.3086144367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ。でも、どりきゅんの二人も参加してくれれば\nいいのに。企画のこと話しても勝手にすればって感じで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7086144367,
      "endTime": 77.271199123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.4581832646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "VENUSグランプリも近いですからね\n再戦をするならそこで、ということなのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4581832646,
      "endTime": 84.5581834553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.7451675969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、次に戦う時は、もちろん私がセンターですわ！\n顔を洗って待っていなさい、どりきゅん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7451675969,
      "endTime": 94.5451675969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.7451675969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら首だと思うけど、すずのセンターもあり\nえるのよね。今日もいい出来だったし負けてられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7451675969,
      "endTime": 105.16516748250001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.3785009303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "センターが二人になったことで、確実に表現の幅も\n広がっていますよね。それぞれの個性が出せていますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3785009303,
      "endTime": 113.49850110189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.6854852436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんもすずちゃんも\nなんだかすっごく大きくなったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6854852436,
      "endTime": 118.34135835149999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.5283424931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、当然ですわ！　私、成長期ですのよ！\n身長だって、すぐに琴乃を追い抜いて差し上げますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5283424931,
      "endTime": 129.7598848896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.9616758265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "今くらいの方が、なでなでしやすくていいけどな～\n芽衣も、もっと大きくならなきゃいけなくなっちゃうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9616758265,
      "endTime": 138.0950040735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 138.2819882152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "なぜ、そこまで撫でようとするんですの！？\nもう、いつか絶対、私が芽衣を撫で回しますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2819882152,
      "endTime": 148.4913529156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.6819882152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは、ソロライブツアーが決まってるよね\nすずちゃんはソロ曲を作るし。どっちも楽しみだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6819882152,
      "endTime": 156.66212441890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.8491085606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "私達も負けていられませんね。一人のアイドルとして\nもっともっと、新たな挑戦をしていかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8491085606,
      "endTime": 164.8597661572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 165.0467502989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　センターの二人に負けないように\n私達も一杯輝かないとね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0467502989,
      "endTime": 170.92981151720002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 171.1167956588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も芽衣も～！　もっともっと見てくれる人を\n笑顔にして、月ストを引っ張っていくよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1167956588,
      "endTime": 178.3858432052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 178.5728273468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_01-suz007.m4a",
